#: ../../chapters/user_interface.rst:1111
msgid "Microphone Controls"
msgstr "Controls de micròfon"

#: ../../chapters/user_interface.rst:1117
msgid "**Talk Button**"
msgstr "**Botó per parlar**"

#: ../../chapters/user_interface.rst:1114
msgid ""
"Hold this button and talk to mix the microphone input into the Mixxx master "
"output. Short click on the button for latching. This is handy for talking "
"for an extended period, for example when :ref:`streaming <live-"
"broadcasting>` a radio show. When in Latch mode, click again to mute the "
"microphone input."
msgstr "Mantingueu premut aquest botó per a que el que digueu es mescli amb la sortida mestra. Feu un clic ràpid al botó si voleu que es quedi activat. Això és pràctic per parlar durant una estona, per exemple quan :ref:`s'emet en viu <live-broadcasting>` un programa de ràdio. Per a desactivar-lo, torneu a prémer el botó."

#: ../../chapters/user_interface.rst:1120
msgid ""
"This control determines the microphone input's mix orientation. Either to "
"the left side of crossfader, to the right side or to the center (default). "
"Clicking cycles through all the options."
msgstr "Aquest control determina la destinació de la mescla de l'entrada de micròfon. Ja sigui al canal esquerra del crossfader, al canal dret, o al centre (per defecte). Feu clic múltiples vegades per canviar entre les diferents possibilitats."

#: ../../chapters/user_interface.rst:1125
msgid "**Microphone Volume Meter**"
msgstr "**Monitor de volum de micròfon**"

#: ../../chapters/user_interface.rst:1125
msgid "This displays the microphone volume input signal strength."
msgstr "Aquí es mostra el nivell de volum de l'entrada de micròfon."

#: ../../chapters/user_interface.rst:1129
msgid "**Microphone Gain Knob**"
msgstr "**Rodeta de guany el micròfon**"

#: ../../chapters/user_interface.rst:1128
msgid ""
"Use this knob to adjust the gain of the microphone output. Try to keep the "
"volume at a reasonable level to avoid signal clipping."
msgstr "Utilitzeu aquesta rodeta per ajustar el guany de la sortida del micròfon. Intenteu mantenir el volum a un nivell raonable per evitar que la senyal es saturi."

#: ../../chapters/user_interface.rst:1134
msgid "Preview Deck Section"
msgstr "La secció del reproductor de pre-escolta"

#: ../../chapters/user_interface.rst:1146
msgid "The Preview Deck with a track loaded"
msgstr "El reproductor de pre-escolta amb una pista carregada"

#: ../../chapters/user_interface.rst:1148
msgid ""
"The Preview Deck is a special deck that allows you to pre-listen to tracks "
"in the headphones before using them in your mix. Pre-listening a track does "
"not change the tracks's :guilabel:`Played` state as well as the play counter"
" and is not logged in the :ref:`History <library-history>`. Press "
":kbd:`CTRL` + :kbd:`4` (Windows/Linux) or :kbd:`CMD` + :kbd:`4` (Mac) to "
"display the Preview Deck."
msgstr "El reproductor de pre-escolta és un reproductor especial que permet escoltar les pistes pels auriculars abans d'utilitzar-les a la mescla. La pre-escolta no canvia l'estat de :guilabel:`Reproduït` ni el comptador de reproduccions, i tampoc es registra a :ref:`l'històric <library-history>`. Premeu :kbd:`CTRL`+ :kbd:`4` (Windows/Linux) o :kbd:`CMD` + :kbd:`4` (Mac) per a mostrar el reproductor de pre-escolta."

#: ../../chapters/user_interface.rst:1154
msgid "The features in detail:"
msgstr "Les característiques en detall:"

#: ../../chapters/user_interface.rst:1156
msgid ""
"**Track Artist/Title**: The artist and title of the track is displayed here."
" This is the same listed under the :guilabel:`Track` and :guilabel:`Title` "
"column in the Mixxx library. This information is initially loaded from the "
"track's :term:`metadata`."
msgstr "**Artista/Títol de la pista**: Es mostra l'artista i el títol de la pista. És el mateix que es mostra a :guilabel:`Pista` i a la columna :guilabel:`Títol` a la biblioteca del Mixxx. Aquesta informació es carrega inicialment de les :term:`metadades <metadata>` de la pista."

#: ../../chapters/user_interface.rst:1161
msgid ""
"**Eject Track button**: Clicking this button ejects the track from the deck."
msgstr ""

#: ../../chapters/user_interface.rst:1164
msgid ""
"**Play/Pause button**: Clicking the button starts and pauses the playback. "
"Right-clicking on the button will stop playback and seek the play position "
"to the beginning of the tracks."
msgstr ""

#: ../../chapters/user_interface.rst:1169
msgid ""
"**Waveform overview**: Shows the various markers (Cues, Hotcues) within the "
"track as well as the waveform envelope of the entire track. Clicking "
"somewhere on the waveform allows you to jump to an arbitrary position in the"
" track."
msgstr "**Gràfic d'ona de la pista**: Mostra diferents marques (punts Cue, Hotcues) de la pista això com l'envolvent de la pista sencera. Feu clic en qualsevol lloc per a anar a aquell punt de la pista."

#: ../../chapters/user_interface.rst:1174
msgid "**Gain slider**: Move the slider to adjust the gain of the track."
msgstr ""

#: ../../chapters/user_interface.rst:1177
msgid ""
"**Volume Meter**: Shows the current volume of the track. If it's too loud "
"and distorted, a peak indicator flashes red."
msgstr ""

#: ../../chapters/user_interface.rst:1181
msgid ""
"For more information, go to the chapter :ref:`library-previewing-tracks`."
msgstr ""
